content.rendered:
Feliks Stamm International – Poland: Awaiting ANABA Team Participation

The prestigious Feliks Stamm International Tournament in Poland is on the horizon, but ANABA has yet to confirm a team for this event. This renowned competition brings together top amateur boxers from around the globe, offering a prime opportunity for athletes to test their skills at an elite level. While no team has been announced, ANABA continues to explore opportunities for future participation. Stay tuned for updates, and keep an eye on upcoming events as we continue to push Australian boxing talent onto the world stage! #FeliksStammInternational #ANABA #AmateurBoxing #Poland2024
